<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>可知杂志</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/rss/test</link><description>Knowable 杂志来自《Annual Reviews》，这是一家非营利性出版商，致力于综合和整合知识，以促进科学进步和造福社会。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>肠道细菌如何与帕金森病相关</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/health-disease/2024/gut-brain-axis-parkinsons-disease-microbiome</link><description>&lt;p&gt;越来越多的证据表明，使人衰弱的神经系统疾病与生活在我们肠道中的微生物之间存在联系。迷走神经可能是一条通路。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/health-disease/2024/gut-brain-axis-parkinsons-disease-microbiome</guid></item><item><title>微生物、情绪和心理健康之间的联系日益密切</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/mind/2024/gut-brain-axis-mental-health-microbiome</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新研究表明，为了保持大脑健康，我们应该照顾肠道微生物组。现在最好的方法不是通过药物和补充剂，而是通过更好的食物。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/mind/2024/gut-brain-axis-mental-health-microbiome</guid></item><item><title>科学家仔细审视幸福研究</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/mind/2024/scientists-scrutinize-happiness-research</link><description>&lt;p&gt;声称揭示了感到快乐的策略的研究值得重新审视&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/mind/2024/scientists-scrutinize-happiness-research</guid></item><item><title>2023 年热门科学故事</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/society/2023/top-scientific-news-and-breakthroughs-of-2023</link><description>&lt;p&gt;动荡的一年中十二个杰出的新闻事件和趋势&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/society/2023/top-scientific-news-and-breakthroughs-of-2023</guid></item><item><title>中美洲火山为地球地质演化提供线索</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/physical-world/2023/central-american-volcanoes-clues-earth-geological-evolution</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从墨西哥到哥斯达黎加，绵延 1,100 公里的中美洲火山弧，这里的岩浆类型多样，形成了地质天堂&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/physical-world/2023/central-american-volcanoes-clues-earth-geological-evolution</guid></item><item><title>为什么科学家正在制造透明木材</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/technology/2023/why-scientists-are-making-transparent-wood</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这种树脂填充材料比塑料更坚固，比玻璃更坚韧，可用于智能手机屏幕、隔热窗等&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/technology/2023/why-scientists-are-making-transparent-wood</guid></item><item><title>新西兰努力拯救圆滚滚、不会飞的鹦鹉</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/living-world/2023/saving-endangered-flightless-birds-of-new-zealand</link><description>DNA 测序、GPS 追踪和定制饮食正在慢慢恢复濒临灭绝的鸮鹦鹉</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/living-world/2023/saving-endangered-flightless-birds-of-new-zealand</guid></item><item><title>尼安德特人：现在比以往任何时候都更加了解</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/society/2023/new-finds-about-neanderthal-brains-and-behavior</link><description>&lt;p&gt;自从我们第一次发现他们的遗骸以来，他们就一直让我们着迷。如今，得益于新的文物和技术，有关我们近亲的发现正在大量而迅速地出现。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/society/2023/new-finds-about-neanderthal-brains-and-behavior</guid></item><item><title>绿色航运提速</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/technology/2023/how-to-turn-the-shipping-industry-green</link><description>一项国际条约旨在到 2050 年左右使航运业实现净零排放。新型燃料、风能和全球范围内的协调能否实现这一目标？</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/technology/2023/how-to-turn-the-shipping-industry-green</guid></item><item><title>冰架解剖和空间激光器</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/newsletter/2023/2023-11-19</link><description>另外，塑料将生物从海岸带到开放水域</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/newsletter/2023/2023-11-19</guid></item></channel></rss>